WEBVTT

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.000
Spy Operation

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:15.000
Can you hear me?
If you can hear my voice, please answer!

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:21.000
Romi! It's the Magic Mirror!
Huh?

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.000
Dianaping... is it really you?

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:34.000
Which student is talking during class?

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:42.000
Principal! Romi is playing with a mirror.
She even brought a pet to school!

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:45.000
Animal?! Ppi!
Shh!

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:53.000
Student Romi! Not only are you always late,
but your attitude in the classroom is also very poor!

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:00.000
Whoa! A cockroach!

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:05.000
Teacher! Are you okay? You were very surprised.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:08.000
Thank you.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:17.000
Dianaping, what exactly happened?

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.000
We were very worried, chu.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:24.000
There's no time. I don't know when the surveillance will start again...

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.000
Surveillance?

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:33.000
What happened to the whereabouts of the Princess Teeniepings I asked you about?

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:37.000
Uh... We already found and caught some of them...

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:43.000
We found Scrubping, Charmingping, Flitterping, Silkyping, and Snowping, chu!

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:48.000
Phew... I'm glad they are all scattered in the town where Princess Romi is.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:53.000
But Dianaping, do you know where you are trapped right now, chu?

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:58.000
I don't know. I can't step a single foot outside of the mirror.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:05.000
Only... I could vaguely see something like a glass window behind Eclipseping...

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:10.000
Judging by that color... This place must be in the Dark Forest...

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:14.000
Dark Forest? I think I've heard of it before, chu?

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:18.000
Oh no, the frequency...

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.000
What's wrong?

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:23.000
I'll contact you again later. The Magic Mirror can communicate at any time...

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:29.000
Dianaping! You contacted the outside world again while I briefly took my eyes off you, didn't you?

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:31.000
No, I didn't do anything...

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:36.000
Liar! I know everything you could possibly think of.

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:42.000
Then stop this foolish act immediately!
Shut up! I don't want to hear your words!

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:52.000
The Dark Forest was once a beautiful forest located north of the Illusion Mountains,
and it's where the castle where the Legend Teenieping lives is located.

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:56.000
If it's a Legend Teenieping...

00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:00.000
Anyway, since we know where it is, let's go save her now!

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:02.000
You cannot.

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:04.000
Why?

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:10.000
The current Dark Forest is so covered in thick fog that you can't tell if it's day or night, so it's very dangerous.

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:15.000
Then are you saying we can't save her even though we know where Dianaping is?

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:24.000
Hmm... There is one way...
Please wait. I've called the kingdom's best spy.

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:28.000
Happying!

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.000
It's been a while, happi!

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:41.000
Happying, departing!

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:58.000
Altitude 20,000 feet, speed no abnormalities, happi!

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:01.000
Uh? What is this, happi!

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:15.000
I can't resist sweet things, posil...

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:18.000
Fluffyping? Why are you here, happi?!

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:24.000
Hi Happying~

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:28.000
What are you doing here instead of the Dessert Village, happi?

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:32.000
I fell asleep while eating a donut earlier...

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:44.000
Wow~

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:55.000
Whoa! Where is this?

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:00.000
Waaah! This isn't the Dessert Village!

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:03.000
What should I do, posil?

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:07.000
We can't turn back, what do we do about this...

00:06:19.000 --> 00:06:20.000
Your Majesty.

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:22.000
What is it?

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:25.000
A suspicious flying object is flying towards the castle.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:30.000
How dare they! I will not let anyone into my castle!

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:34.000
Nihil Nihiles! Nihil Nihilera!

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:43.000
Wh-what?

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:47.000
Why a sudden lightning, posil!

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:52.000
Tsk, have we been spotted? Hold on tight!

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.000
Good.

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:11.000
We have to escape right now, happi!

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:13.000
Going!

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:25.000
We lived, posil...

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:30.000
This is the forest leading to the Mirror Castle!

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:35.000
You wait here until I come back, happi!

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:41.000
B-but... Happying, let's go together, posil!

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:46.000
It's too scary here, posil...

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:58.000
That is the Mirror Castle. It's too much for you to climb up, so this time, really wait here, happi!

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:18.000
Posil!

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:22.000
You, how did you...

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:27.000
Secret! I can handle myself too, posil!

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:31.000
If you say so...

00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:36.000
No Fluffyping!

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:49.000
I lived, posil...

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:54.000
Where is this... That's...

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:58.000
Happying! Happying! Happying!

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:10.000
Who is this? The owner of this castle?

00:09:29.000 --> 00:09:35.000
What? It's just a mirror. Who is it? If you don't come out right now, I'll shoot, happi!

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:42.000
Violence is bad. I surrender, so please forgive me.

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:47.000
You are the Magic Mirror! Where on earth did you hide Dianaping!

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:49.000
H-Here!

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:54.000
Liar! That's Dianaping?!

00:09:56.000 --> 00:10:01.000
You fell for it. To think the uninvited guest who broke into my castle was after Dianaping!

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:04.000
You are Eclipseping!

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:10.000
You're a Teenieping I've never seen before. Isn't it polite to introduce yourself if you enter someone else's castle?

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:15.000
I am Happying of the Emotion Kingdom! I will take Dianaping with me!

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:18.000
Try it if you can!

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:35.000
Quite fast.

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:44.000
For a kingdom's spy, you're lackluster. Is this all you've got?

00:10:45.000 --> 00:10:47.000
What exactly did you do to Dianaping?!

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:49.000
You don't need to know!

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:51.000
I'm fine, so run away!

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:56.000
Shut up! I'll lock you in the mirror too! Nihil Nihilera!

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:03.000
Nihil Nihil Nihilera!

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:11.000
Happying, are you okay posil?

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:14.000
Happying, I'm here posil!

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:20.000
I saw from the hallway, that's the only place we can escape posil! Come on, hurry!

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:23.000
But Dianaping...

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:34.000
They got away!

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:37.000
Are you hurt anywhere?

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:43.000
Of course not! Wait, since when was this scratch here?

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:48.000
Well... I didn't know. When did this happen?

00:11:57.000 --> 00:12:01.000
Thank you Fluffyping. I survived thanks to you.

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:06.000
I'm sorry for being a burden to you posil...

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:13.000
Since we've grasped the location of the castle, we must prepare properly and definitely save Dianaping next time.

00:12:14.000 --> 00:12:16.000
Yeah! Right posil!

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:28.000
I can't tell where we are anymore posil.

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:35.000
Eclipseping, she's a scary opponent. Let's go back Fluffyping.

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:41.000
I won't leave them alone!